Text.Value: In that case, you are most welcome. Lord Gortash will want to see you immediately.
Attack.
You were not asked to find her. You were asked to kill her.
Entry is prohibited, citizen. Vacate the premises immediately.
Turn away, citizen. The penalties for trespass are severe.
Back away, citizen. This is an order.
Citizen Fluffington, I advise caution. This area is restricted, under orders of Lord Enver Gortash.
Lord Gortash will be informed - if you were to kill her and bring her Netherstone, he would be most pleased to reacquaint himself with you.
I have a report from the Steel Watch Foundry.
This area is restricted, under orders of Lord Enver Gortash. Intruders are subject to deadly force.
Leave.
I have located Orin.
State your business.
Lord Gortash is expecting me.
Bold. Foolish. Futile.
I have Orin's Netherstone.
Leave.
Lord Gortash does not have time for this. File your report through the ordinary channels.
My business is private.
I have Orin's Netherstone.
Assassination. Orin sent me to kill Gortash.
Do not test Lord Gortash's patience. Return with the Netherstone.
Then I presume it is also insignificant. Good day.
I'm here on behalf of Orin the Red - Gortash dies today.
You test Lord Gortash's patience. Return with Orin's Netherstone, or do not return at all.
Your tongue says one thing, your mind says the opposite. You lie.
You have chosen non-compliance. Your next of kin will be notified of your offence and elimination.

Synopsis: Steel Watcher stops you from going to the roof.
